\q1 Assign ye greatness to our God. 
\q1
\v 4  \add As for\add* God, his works \add are\add* true, 
\q1 And all his ways \add are\add* judgment: 
\q1 God \add is\add* faithful, and there is no unrighteousness \add in him\add*; 
\q1 Just and holy \add is\add* the Lord. 
\q1
\v 5 They have sinned, not \add pleasing\add* him; spotted children, 
\q1 A froward and perverse generation. 
\q1
