\q1 They sucked honey out of the rock, 
\q1 And oil out of the solid rock. 
\q1
\v 14 Butter of cows, and milk of sheep, 
\q1 With the fat of lambs and rams, 
\q1 Of calves and kids, 
\q1 With fat of kidneys of wheat; 
\q1 And he drank wine, the blood of the grape. 
\q1
