\q1
\v 21 They have provoked me to jealousy with \add that which is\add* not God, 
\q1 They have exasperated me with their idols; 
\q1 And I will provoke them to jealousy with them that are no nation, 
\q1 I will anger them with a nation void of understanding. 
\q1
