\q1 And their vine-branch of Gomorrah: 
\q1 Their grape \add is\add* a grape of gall, 
\q1 Their cluster \add is\add* one of bitterness. 
\q1
\v 33 Their wine \add is\add* the rage of serpents, 
\q1 And the incurable rage of asps. 
\q1
