\q1 And ye drank the wine of their drink offerings? 
\q1 Let them arise and help you, 
\q1 And be your protectors. 
\q1
\v 39 Behold, behold that I am \add he\add*, 
\q1 And there is no god beside me: 
\q1 I kill, and I will make to live: 
\q1 I will smite, and I will heal; 
