\c 34  
\p
\v 1 And Moses went up from Araboth Moab to the mount of Nebo, to the top of Pisgah, which is before Jericho; and the Lord showed him all the mount of Gilead to Dan, and all the land of Naphtali, 
\v 2 and all the land of Ephraim and Manasseh, and all the land of Judah to the farthest sea; 
